1763年的'''巴黎和约'''是[[七年战争|七年战争]]的交战双方于1763年2月10日在[[法国|法国]][[巴黎|巴黎]]签订的[[和约|和约]]，标志着七年战争的结束。条约规定，法国将整个[[法屬加拿大|法屬加拿大]]（[[圣皮埃尔和密克隆群岛|圣皮埃尔和密克隆群岛]]除外）、[[法屬路易斯安那|法屬路易斯安那]]中[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]以東部分割给[[英国|英国]]，并从[[印度|印度]]撤出，只保留[[法屬印度|5个市镇]]。[[法國|法國]]亦承認[[英國|英國]]對[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]、[[格林納達|格林納達]]、[[聖文森特和格林納丁斯|聖文森特和格林納丁斯]]以及[[多巴哥|多巴哥]]的主權<ref name=paris-4>"His Most Christian Majesty cedes and guaranties to his said Britannick Majesty, in full right, Canada, with all its dependencies, as well as the island of Cape Breton, and all the other islands and coasts in the gulph and river of St. Lawrence, and in general, every thing that depends on the said countries, lands, islands, and coasts, with the sovereignty, property, possession, and all rights acquired by treaty, or otherwise, which the Most Christian King and the Crown of France have had till now over the said countries, lands, islands, places, coasts, and their inhabitants" – Article IV of the [[File:Wikisource-logo.svg|12px]] [[wikisource:Treaty_of_Paris_(1763)|Treaty of Paris (1763)]] at [[Wikisource|Wikisource]]</ref> 。[[西班牙|西班牙]]割[[佛罗里达|佛罗里达]]给英国。

